The refugees from Acedia have arrived
and we're doing what we can in the
base to deal with them.

rows.label: tlk45320122_05_msg0002
rows.name:
From what I heard, Iira attacked
them with some Divine Beast-like...thing.

rows.label: tlk45320122_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Two Divine Beasts fighting each other...
It's the stuff of nightmares.

rows.label: tlk45320122_05_msg0004
rows.name:
There's rumors Superbia's moved
up near the World Tree as well...

rows.label: tlk45320122_05_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm worried for my dad back in the
home country. I hope he'll agree to
evacuate here too...
